{"type":"message","id":"f796738d","parentId":"d587c252","timestamp":"2026-04-16T12:59:19.340Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The gateway is listening on port 3100 but returning 404 on all these routes. Let me try to find the actual API routes by checking the gateway's actual behavior. Let me look at the gateway source code to understand the API structure, or try WebSocket connections.\n\nActually, let me take a different approach. The user is experiencing slow message display. This is a webchat channel issue. Let me look at the webchat channel implementation to understand the polling mechanism.\n\nActually wait - let me re-read what I know. The user said the messages they send take 5s-1min to appear on screen. And my replies are also slow. Both directions are slow.\n\nThe Control UI webchat uses a specific mechanism to communicate with the gateway. \n\nI'm checking whether this is a WebSocket connection issue or a gateway processing bottleneck. The session status shows `systemSent: true`, indicating my last response was queued, so the gateway is actively processing. Let me examine the gateway's WebSocket implementation directly.\n\nI think I've been going in circles with the gateway code when I should focus on the Control UI side. The user's messages are taking 5 seconds to 1 minute to appear after they send them—that's the actual problem. This could be a Control UI polling interval issue, or the gateway might not be pushing messages through WebSocket properly. Let me check if the Control UI is using polling instead of a direct WebSocket connection.\n\nLooking at the changelog, the 4.14 release replaced marked.js with markdown-it to fix a ReDoS vulnerability that was freezing the Control UI. If the UI is now spending more CPU processing markdown, it could be lagging when displaying messages. But that's rendering performance, not the delay in messages appearing in the first place. I should check if the Control UI is actually polling for new messages and how frequently.","thinkingSignature":"3f43d85bf2d820d6c12724062cdf86032f9c8e830e9cdacca40a0c3dd97171fb"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_cbf7522287394137b4492e78","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find /home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw -name \"*.js\" 2>/dev/null | xargs grep -l \"web"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_202e49dcf6a244c686b80963","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls /home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/ | grep -i \"webchat\\|channel\" | head -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":148,"output":519,"cacheRead":61184,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":61851,"cost":{"input":0.000044399999999999995,"output":0.0006228,"cacheRead":0.0036710399999999995,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004338239999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776344344970,"responseId":"06301019b967325d4b45c09c7de77bbf"}}
