{"type":"message","id":"14872da4","parentId":"edf551ee","timestamp":"2026-04-16T13:02:22.197Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Port 3100 is the Control UI. Let me look at the gateway process more carefully to understand the webchat channel mechanism.\n\nActually, let me step back and think about this more simply. The user is using the OpenClaw Control UI (webchat at port 3100). The Control UI communicates with the gateway (port 3102) via WebSocket.\n\nThe delay could be:\n1. Control UI polling gateway for new messages (polling interval)\n2. Gateway processing delay\n3. Network latency\n\nLooking at the CHANGELOG, the most relevant change for webchat polling behavior in 4.14 is:\n- \"Agents/context engine: compact engine-owned sessions from the first tool-loop delta and preserve ingest fallback when `afterTurn` is absent, so long-running tool loops can stay bounded without dropping engine state.\"\n\n\n- \"Agents/context engines: run opt-in turn maintenance as idle-aware background work so the next foreground turn no longer waits on proactive maintenance.\"\n\nThat second one is key—turn maintenance should now run in the background so it doesn't block the next request. But the user is experiencing delay on both sent and received messages, which suggests the issue might be in the Control UI itself rather than the gateway. The 5-second-to-1-minute range they mentioned points to something specific in the webchat channel implementation.\n\nLet me check if there's a heartbeat mechanism in the Control UI's JavaScript that's creating this bottleneck.","thinkingSignature":"d98e3688f44c7376b58b50c5a7517df38e2f2d9269e5b83ee7f8583797e3f466"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a7f1cfa2565344939f846992","name":"process","arguments":{"action":"kill","sessionId":"fresh-daisy"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1030,"output":330,"cacheRead":65408,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66768,"cost":{"input":0.000309,"output":0.000396,"cacheRead":0.003924479999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004629479999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776344523597,"responseId":"063010ca44d8cc3a4ded739e51f357f0"}}
