{"type":"message","id":"25fb84f4","parentId":"2405d1df","timestamp":"2026-04-16T13:21:44.075Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to do a comprehensive deep inspection of the framework using subagents. Let me read the SOUL.md v10.1 thinking section first as required, then spawn multiple subagents to investigate the slowdown issue from different angles.\n\nThe user is asking about a comprehensive framework inspection related to the slowdown issue. Let me use the taskflow/coding-agent skill approach - spawn multiple subagents in parallel to investigate different aspects.\n\nLet me think about what angles to investigate:\n1. Gateway WebSocket/SSE connection handling (Control UI side)\n2. Session/message queue processing (Gateway side)\n3. The 4.14 changelog changes that could affect latency\n\n\n4. Bootstrap/initialization flow changes\n5. Context engine changes\n\nI'll spawn multiple subagents to investigate these different angles in parallel.","thinkingSignature":"77fb60b4aee11b6828b3d4f8f42dbaed635f5f5f6dcae5607a3feabacd5b28c2"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b007d552b3784a81846c1be5","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"mode":"run","runtime":"subagent","task":"任务：审查 OpenClaw 4.14 版本变更对 webchat/control-ui 响应延迟的影响。\n\n项目路径：/home/ai/.openclaw\n框架包：/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw\n\n**重点排查方向：**\n\n1. **4.14 changelog 中可能影响延迟的改动**：\n   - \"Agents/context engines: compact engine-owned sessions from the first tool-loop delta\" — 这个 compact 逻辑是否在每轮都触发？\n   - \"Gateway/sessions: stop heartbeat, cron-event, and exec-event turns from overwriting shared-session routing\" — 这个改动是否影响 session 状态更新？\n   - \"UI/chat: replace marked.js with markdown-it\" — 这个渲染变化是否增加了处理时间？\n\n2. **Bootstrap 链路**：SOUL.md v10.1 重构后，bootstrap 文件的加载顺序和注入方式是否有变化？是否每次 /new 都会重复加载？\n\n3. **Session 状态**：当前 session (agent:main:main) 的 childSessions 有 142 个，这些子 session 是否在每次消息时都被遍历处理？\n\n4. **Context engine turn maintenance*